The evidence with the title 'The Travis Letter returns! - Travis ' says Landholder: Travis owned land in Ben Milam and Stephen F. Austin's colonies. Slaveholder : his slave Joe went to the Alamo with him but survived the battle  ... Of cavalry by general Stephen F. Austin , and later promoted to captain .  ... Once at the Alamo , he shared command with colonel James Bowie until Bowie fell ill . 
